summary: Hello there! I am Jorge, and this site is under construction!

As part of the NeurIPS 2019 Reproducibility Challenge, we chose to attempt to reproduce the attack algorithm proposed in "Subspace Attack: Exploiting Promising Subspaces for Query-Efficient Black-box Attacks". Our reported results are better than the original paper in terms of the median number of queries per attack, but worse in terms of failure rate. A concise assessment of our implementation is also included.
title: [Re] Subspace Attack: Exploiting Promising Subspaces for Query-Efficient Black-box Attacks

content: Pindery is a cross-platform social network designed to join and organise parties. Each user will have the possibility to create a new party or join already existing ones nearby.
summary: A cross-platform social network designed to join and organize parties.
title: Pindery
